annotation.text:
There are a lot of different versions existing with Imprint :
Made in Holland 

This one has had an additional Sticker at the german version :
Die Musik aus
der RTL TELEVISION Serie 
HIGHLANDER
ES KANN NUR 
EINE GEBEN!
(This should have readed and printed instead EINEN.) 

This Release was pressed with a lot of different Matrix / Runout Versions, wich have the same beginning:
CDP 746267 2 AR @ 1 1-1-7-NL
CDP 746267 2 AR @ 1 1-1-11-NL
CDP 746267 2 AR @ 1 1-1-17-NL
CDP 746267 2 AR @ 1 1-1-18-NL
CDP 746267 2 AR @ 1 1-1-20-NL
CDP 746267 2 AR @ 1 1-3-22-NL
(The Versions with a higher number than a 1 after the '@' are probably later released Reissues.)
